===== 配置kibana
[source, bash]
----
vim /etc/kibana/kibana.yml

#在配置文件中修改相关项
server.host: "0.0.0.0"
server.publicBaseUrl: "http://node01:5601/"
server.name: "node01"
----

===== 启动kibana
[source, bash]
----
systemctl enable --now kibana
----

